<manpage>
    <volume> 常用数据结构 </volume>
    <interface>AStringBuf</interface>
    <method> GetCapacity </method>

    <description>
        <para> 返回此对象数据区可容纳的字符个数。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax_nopara>
        <return_val> Int32 </return_val>
        <modifier>const</modifier>
        <NoArguments/>
    </syntax_nopara>

    <return>
        <para>AStringBuf对象数据区可容纳的字符个数。</para>
    </return>
    <remarks>
        <para>如果AStringBuf的m_pBuf 指针为空则返回0。</para>
    </remarks>
<example>
<pre>
AStringBuf_&lt;10&gt; asbuf;  
asbuf.Copy("a");
CConsole::WriteLine(asbuf.GetCapacity()); //Display : 10
CConsole::WriteLine(asbuf.GetLength()); //Display : 1
CConsole::WriteLine(asbuf.GetAvailableSpace()); //Display : 9

asbuf.SetEmpty();
asbuf.Copy("中");
CConsole::WriteLine(asbuf.GetCapacity()); //Display : 10
CConsole::WriteLine(asbuf.GetLength()); //Display : 2
CConsole::WriteLine(asbuf.GetAvailableSpace()); //Display : 8
</pre>
</example>
